About Me 
  
  
  




Hi, This is Emma.


    
        I study both Computer Science and Statistics as my majors, and I am currently a third year student from the university of toronto.
        I hold great enthusiasm in topics related to my field and is especially interested in Data Analysis and Software Engineering. 
        Playing badminton and kayaking are my favourite activities for relaxation, and I have a solid plan to expand this list soon.
        dwz92
        Emma Teng
        e.teng@nail.utoronto.ca
